query: SELECT p.id, p.leadId, p.addressLine1, p.dealMachinePropertyId, COUNT(c.id) as contact_count FROM properties p LEFT JOIN contacts c ON c.propertyId = p.id WHERE p.addressLine1 LIKE '%1711 Nw 55th%' GROUP BY p.id;
